{"title":"LUUV","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eLUUV’s beauty products are characterized by efficiency and clean ingredients. LUUV uses many plants that grow in northern climate like sea buckthorn, birch, cranberry, plum, barley, hone These have shaped the product lines – energizing vitamin-booster products from the oil of sea buckthorn, balancing products from birch extract, age-defying products with cranberries and softening products with honey.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","products":[{"product_id":"luuv-natural-volumizing-shampoo-250ml","title":"LUUV Natural Volumizing Seabuckthorn Shampoo 250ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNatural shampoo enriched with sea buckthorn oil is natural and gentle, which gives hair fluffiness and shine. Sea buckthorn oil strengthens the hair, provides the necessary nutrients to the hair and scalp, and helps prevent split ends. Wheat protein strengthens hair, stimulates hair growth and increases hair fluffiness and elasticity. Essential oils contribute to the normal functioning of the sebum secretion of the scalp and give a feeling of freshness.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003esuitable for all hair types, including oily hair\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eprovides natural volume\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ewith cleansing effect\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003egives hair fluffiness and shine\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003emoisturizes and strengthens the hair\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ewith a citrus scent\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eseabuckthorn oil to nourish the hair\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003emade with natural cleansers\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003egentle on the scalp\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e98,58% natural ingredients\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | vegan\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply the shampoo thoroughly on wet hair. Massage into a lather. Rinse. Repeat the procedure, if necessary.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Cetearyl Alcohol, Lecithin, Sodium Cetearyl Sulfate, Vegetable Oil, Panthenol, Cetyl Alcohol, PCA Glyceryl Oleate, Ricinus Communis Seed (Castor) Oil, Glycerin, Hippophae Rhamnoides (Sea Buckthorn) oil, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Glyceryl Stearate, Citric Acid, Tocopherol (E-vitamin), Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Parfum, Linalool\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51110474252615,"sku":null,"price":11.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-natural-volumizing-seabuckthorn-shampoo-250ml-549035.png?v=1740891413"},{"product_id":"luuv-natural-softening-honey-shampoo-250ml","title":"LUUV Natural Softening Honey Shampoo 250ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNatural honey shampoo makes the hair soft and easy to comb, nourishing the hair from roots to ends. Organic honey extract makes the hair silky and protects from environmental effects. Organic barley extract stimulates hair growth and gives shine. Wheat protein strengthens the hair and increases elasticity. Also suitable for colored hair.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003esuitable for all hair types, including dyed hair\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003estrengthens hair from root to tip\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ewith a softening and protective effect\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003egives hair softness\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eimproves hair structure \u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ewith a honey-sweet smell\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003egentle on the scalp\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003emade with mild, plant-based cleansers\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ewith natural bee glue extract\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e99,22% natural ingredients\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply the shampoo thoroughly on wet hair. Massage into a lather. Rinse. Repeat the procedure, if necessary.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Coco-Glucoside, Sodium Coco-Sulfate, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Betaine, Citric Acid, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil, Propolis (Bee glue) extract, Panthenol, Hordeum Vulgare (Barlay) Extract, Glyceryl Oleate, Guar Hydroxypropyltrimonium Chloride, Glycerin, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Parfum\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51110637044039,"sku":null,"price":11.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-natural-softening-honey-shampoo-250ml-212888.png?v=1740891413"},{"product_id":"luuv-natural-caring-shampoo-250ml","title":"LUUV Natural Caring Shampoo with Plum Oil 250ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eLUUV natural shampoo with plum oil is suitable for everyday use for all hair types. Cold-pressed plum kernel oil moisturizes both the scalp and hair and protects hair from heat treatment. Natural betaine and aloe keep hair moisturized. Natural gentle plum shampoo makes hair well combed, silky and elastic. Suitable for both coloured and natural hair.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003esuitable for all hair types, including dyed hair and curly hair\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ewith caring and softening effect\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003emoisturizes and protects your hair\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eprotects hair from heat treatment\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003emild, plant-based cleansers\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003egentle on the scalp\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003egentle enough for everyday use\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ewith organic plum oil for a silky finish\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e99,18% natural ingredients\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | paraben free | vegan\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply the shampoo thoroughly on wet hair. Massage into a lather. Rinse. Repeat the procedure, if necessary.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Coco-Glucoside, Sodium Lauryl Glucose Carboxylate (and) Lauryl Glucoside, Oryza Sativa (Rice) Starch, Cocamidoprpyl Betaine, Glycerin, Betaine, Prunus Domestica (Plum) Seed oil, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Guar Hydroxypropyltrimonium Chloride, Sodium Benzoate (and) Potassium Sorbate, Coco-Glucoside (and) Glyceryl Oleate, Cymbopogon Martini (Palmarosa) oil, Citric Acid, Parfum\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51110671745351,"sku":null,"price":11.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-natural-caring-shampoo-with-plum-oil-250ml-277927.png?v=1740891412"},{"product_id":"luuv-natural-energizing-shower-gel-250ml","title":"LUUV Natural Energizing Carrot Shower Gel 250ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eImagine stepping into your shower and being greeted by a burst of citrusy goodness that awakens your senses and puts a smile on your face every morning. That’s exactly what this shower gel delivers with its pleasant citrus scent that’s bound to become your new favorite. But it’s more than just a fragrant delight. This shower gel is formulated to effectively remove dirt and grime, leaving your skin squeaky clean and revitalized. It also deeply moisturizes your skin, ensuring that you step out of the shower feeling as soft and smooth as a carrot straight from the garden.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe key ingredient is pure carrot oil, a rich source of essential vitamins that work wonders for your skin. It enhances skin elasticity, helping you maintain that youthful glow you’ve always wanted. Make it an essential part of your well-scented bathroom routine, and let the rejuvenating power of carrots and citrus awaken your senses and delight you every single day. Showering has never been this enjoyable!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMoisturizing\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eImproves skin elasticity\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eRefreshing citrus scent\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cspan\u003eFor all skin types\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eKey ingredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eCoco-Glucoside\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003eis a detergent, 100% natural (derived from coconut), environmentally friendly and certified. The detergent is gentle – also suitable for sensitive skin and children.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eCarrot oil\u003c\/span\u003e (specifically carrot seed oil) contains a lot of carotene, which gives a complexion-enhancing effect. Carrot oil is always in a carrier oil (i.e., diluted) because it is too intense on its own. It contains a lot of vitamin A. The natural SPF of carrot oil is around 40, but since it is diluted, it ends up around SPF 10.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | vegan\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply the shower gel on damp skin with light circular movements, rinse and dry.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Coco-Glucoside, Sodium Lauryl Glucose Carboxylate (and) Lauryl Glucoside, Oryza Sativa (Rice) Starch, Cocamidoprpyl Betaine, Glycerin, Betaine, Prunus Domestica (Plum) Seed oil, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Guar Hydroxypropyltrimonium Chloride, Sodium Benzoate (and) Potassium Sorbate, Coco-Glucoside (and) Glyceryl Oleate, Cymbopogon Martini (Palmarosa) oil, Citric Acid, Parfum\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51110691897671,"sku":null,"price":10.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-natural-energizing-carrot-shower-gel-250ml-522072.png?v=1740560025"},{"product_id":"luuv-natural-exfoliating-shower-gel-250ml","title":"LUUV Natural Exfoliating Shower Gel 250ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eNatural Exfoliating Shower Gel – the ultimate way to rejuvenate your skin and start your day with a refreshing burst of energy. This invigorating shower gel offers a dual-action formula that gently exfoliates and cleanses, leaving your skin irresistibly fresh and radiant.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDesigned with your skin’s well-being in mind, our formula ensures a gentle exfoliation that sweeps away dead skin cells without causing any micro damage. Feel confident knowing that bamboo particles are not only kind to your skin but also eco-friendly, embracing the values of both beauty and sustainability. As the bamboo particles delicately scrub away impurities, they also awaken your skin’s natural renewal process, fostering improved elasticity and texture. Experience the joy of skin that feels irresistibly soft and smooth to the touch, every single day. The light and fresh scent of green tea not only invigorates your senses but also sets the stage for a perfect start to your day.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis exfoliating shower gel isn’t just a treat for the ladies – it’s versatile design caters to the dynamic lifestyles of both genders, making it an ideal addition to any daily routine. Welcome each day with skin that’s fresh, vibrant, and ready to take on the world.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eGentle, but effective\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cspan\u003eDoesn\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e‘\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003et dry skin\u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFor daily use\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFresh green tea scent\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cspan\u003eSafe for the environment\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eKey ingredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eCoco-Glucoside\u003c\/span\u003e is a detergent, 100% natural (derived from coconut), environmentally friendly and certified. The detergent is gentle – also suitable for sensitive skin and children.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | vegan\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply the shower gel on damp skin with light circular movements, rinse and dry.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Coco-Glucoside, Bambusa Vulgaris powder, Vegetable Glycerin, Citric Acid, Xanthan Gum, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Parfum\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51110715982151,"sku":null,"price":10.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-natural-exfoliating-shower-gel-250ml-332480.png?v=1740725717"},{"product_id":"luuv-nourishing-and-protecting-honey-cream-200ml","title":"LUUV Nourishing and Protecting Honey Cream 200ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eThis little jar of joy is here to transform your skincare routine into a blissful and nourishing experience. Imagine a velvety smooth cream that not only pampers your skin but also creates a natural shield against whatever life throws at it. With the power of beeswax, this cream becomes your skin’s ultimate superhero, protecting it from harsh water and challenging climates. No need to worry about dryness either, as it is also packed with the goodness of nourishing shea butter. And it’s not just about the benefits – the sweet aroma of honey is pure bliss for your body and senses.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWith consistent use, watch as your skin transforms into a softer, smoother, and more resilient version of itself. It’s like unlocking the secret to youthful, radiant skin – you’ll be glowing with confidence! Tailored specifically for dry, very dry, and mature skin, this cream is here to turn your skincare routine into a joyful self-care ritual. It’s the perfect companion for those seeking an extra boost of hydration and love.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTo top it all off, it carries the globally recognized ECOCERT \/ COSMOS certification. Feel confident knowing that you’re treating your skin to the finest, most natural ingredients out there. Your skin deserves this blissful treat, and you deserve to feel radiant and revitalized.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSilky and foamy texture\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDeeply moisturizing\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFor dry and mature skin\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSweet honey aroma\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eSuitable for everyday use. Apply cream to clean skin and rub in circular motions until absorbed.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Cocos Nucifera Oil, Polyglyceryl-3 Distearate, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter, Glyceryl Stearate SE, Cera Alba (Beeswax), Glycerin, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil, Propolis (Bee glue) extract, Hippophae Rhamnoides Fruit Oil, Glyceryl Caprylate, Citrus Aurantium Dulcis (Orange) Oil, Xanthan Gum, Tocopherol, Triethyl Citrate, Benzoic Acid, Aroma, Citral, D-limonene, Linalool\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51110748717383,"sku":null,"price":15.6,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-nourishing-and-protecting-honey-cream-200ml-311638.png?v=1740560031"},{"product_id":"luuv-deep-moisture-soft-plum-body-cream-200ml","title":"LUUV Deep Moisture Soft Plum Body Cream 200ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eSay hello to plum perfection – introducing delightful LUUV Natural Deeply Moisturizing Body Cream with Plum Oil! Infused with the nourishing goodness of plum oil and coconut oil, this cream brings balance and harmony to your skin’s moisture levels while warding off any external foes that dare to challenge your skin’s health! Let’s talk about the star ingredient: cold-pressed plum seed oil. Bursting with vitamins A, C, and E, it’s a powerhouse of nourishment for your skin. This oil is also packed with omega fatty acids that restore and replenish skin, leaving it feeling oh-so-soft and supple. And let’s not forget the delightful touch of cranberry extract, a powerful antioxidant that fights the signs of aging, giving your skin a youthful and radiant appearance.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWith its foamy texture and fast absorption, this cream ensures that your skin feels pampered without any greasy residue or clogged pores. It’s a perfect match even for those with sensitive skin, providing gentle care and nourishment. So, let the enchanting aroma of plums dance around you as you embrace the joy of smooth, nourished, and glowing skin!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eLight foamy texture\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDeeply moisturizing\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eQuickly absorbing\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSuitable for sensitive skin\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMild plum scent\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | paraben free | vegan\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eSuitable for everyday use. Apply cream to clean skin and rub in circular motions until absorbed.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Cocos nucifera oil, Mangifera indica seed (Mango) butter, Polyglyceryl-3 Distearate, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate, Hydrolyzed wheat protein, Prunus domestica (Plum) seed oil, Cetyl alcohol, Vaccinium Macrocarpon fruit (Cranberry) extract, Triethyl Citrate, Glyceryl Caprylate, Benzoic Acid, Xanthan gum, Parfum, Mica, Titanium dioxide, CI 77491\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51110775652679,"sku":null,"price":19.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-deep-moisture-soft-plum-body-cream-200ml-412185.png?v=1740560030"},{"product_id":"luuv-deep-moisture-soft-plum-body-cream-200ml-copy","title":"LUUV Energizing vitamin body cream 200ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eEnriched with the goodness of sea buckthorn, this body cream works wonders in softening and revitalizing your skin. Suitable for all skin types, it’s a true game-changer in your skincare routine. Indulge in the luxurious touch of mango butter as it effortlessly nourishes and hydrates, leaving your skin irresistibly silky and smooth.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBrace yourself for the true vitamin explosion from the sea buckthorn oil, packed with vitamins A and C. These powerful antioxidants work their magic, giving your skin the ultimate boost it deserves. At the same time, carrot oil restores vitality and radiance, giving your complexion a natural glow that’s simply breathtaking. Whether you have dry or oily skin, our body cream works wonders in balancing it out, all while keeping your pores clear and free. But the true magic happens when you look in the mirror – a beautiful, glowing complexion that radiates with vitality and health.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eLight foamy texture\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSoftens and nourishes\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFor all skin types\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFresh citrus aroma\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | paraben free | vegan\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eSuitable for everyday use. Apply cream to clean skin and rub in circular motions until absorbed.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Cocos Nucifera, Mangifera Indica seed (Mango) butter, Polyglyceryl-3 Distearate, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Cetyl Alcohol, Dunaliella Salina (Carrot) Extract, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil, Hippophae Rhamnoides (Sea buckthorn) oil, Citrus Nobilis (Mandarin oil), Citrus Aurantium (Orange oil), Triethylcitrate, Glyceryl Caprylate, Xanthan Gum, Benzoic Acid, Parfum, Limonene, Citral, Linalool\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51110840041799,"sku":null,"price":19.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-energizing-vitamin-body-cream-200ml-663135.png?v=1740560032"},{"product_id":"luuv-natural-kids-shower-foam-150ml","title":"LUUV Natural Kids Shower Foam 150ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eThis is LUUV kids shower foam – the ultimate bath-time companion that brings joy, playfulness, and eco-consciousness to your little one’s daily routine! Certified with the leading ECOCERT \/ COSMOS eco-certificate, this delightful foam will make showering an adventure filled with laughter and fun.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWe understand that your child’s delicate skin deserves only the best, which is why this shower foam is crafted from carefully selected detergents that are gentle and won’t irritate your child’s precious skin. The sweet and juicy pear aroma is completely derived from natural sources, ensuring a captivating scent without any allergens. As for the vibrant pinkish purple color, a surprising secret ingredient is used – potato extract! That’s right, this eco-certified formula uses this natural wonder to create a mesmerizing hue that will captivate your child’s imagination. It’s like a burst of colorful magic in every pump!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNatural and allergen-free\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFresh pear scent\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDoes not irritate or dry skin\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | vegan | certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply the shower gel on damp skin with light circular movements, rinse and dry.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Glycerin, Coco-Glucoside, Ipomoea Batatas (Potato) Root Extract, Cetyl Alcohol, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Citric Acid, Aroma, Acacia Senegal Gum, Maltodextrin\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51111034487111,"sku":null,"price":10.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-natural-kids-shower-foam-150ml-609563.png?v=1740891412"},{"product_id":"luuv-natural-kids-shampoo-250ml","title":"LUUV Natural Kids Shampoo 250ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eLUUV natural kids shampoo  – where fun meets healthy hair! This shampoo takes your child’s hair care to new heights with its completely natural, tear-free formula. Designed for little adventurers, it leaves hair strong, shiny, and gently detangles even the most resistant knots. With ECOCERT\/COSMOS eco-certificate, you can trust that LUUV kids shampoo is not only gentle on your little one’s hair but also on the environment.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCarefully selected herbal detergents are perfect for your child’s delicate scalp, ensuring a nurturing and soothing wash. Shampoo is also infused with the goodness of moisturizing aloe and plant betaine – not only does it make their hair easy to comb, but it also strengthens it from root to tip, leaving it looking healthy, vibrant, and ready for any adventure that comes their way. The sweet and juicy pear aroma is naturally derived and allergen-free. LUUV natural kids shampoo is not only natural but also vegan, making it a choice you can feel great about. Experience hair that’s as soft as a mother’s caress and join the fun today!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNatural and allergen-free\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eTear-free formula\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFresh pear scent\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDoes not irritate skin\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eECOCERT\/COSMOS certified\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNatural origin 98,4%\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | vegan | certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply the shampoo thoroughly on wet hair. Massage into a lather. Rinse. Repeat the procedure, if necessary.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Coco-Glucoside, Sodium Lauryl Glucose Carboxylate, Lauryl Glucoside, Oryza Sativa (Rice) Starch, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice, Betaine, Guar Hydroxypropyltrimonium Chloride, Citric Acid, Glyceryl Oleate, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Aroma\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51115336728903,"sku":null,"price":11.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-natural-kids-shampoo-250ml-163262.png?v=1740891417"},{"product_id":"luuv-natural-kids-bubble-bath-200ml","title":"LUUV Natural Kids Bubble Bath 200ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eTransform your child’s bath time into a delightful adventure with LUUV pear bath foam for kids! This incredible bath foam is not only certified with the prestigious ECOCERT \/ COSMOS eco-certificate, but it also adds a touch of magic and excitement to every bathing experience. The rich and velvety soft foam, derived from carefully selected herbal detergents, caresses your little one’s delicate skin without causing any irritation or dryness. And the delicious pear aroma? It’s all-natural, creating a truly mouth-watering bathing experience.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNatural and allergen-free\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFresh pear scent\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDoes not irritate or dry skin\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eECOCERT\/COSMOS certified\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNatural origin 98,72%\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | vegan | certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eJust add this magical foam to warm running water, and let the enchanting bath time adventure begin!\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Coco-Glucoside, Sodium Coco-Sulfate, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Aroma, Glyceryl Oleate, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Citric Acid\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51115356291399,"sku":null,"price":11.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-natural-kids-bubble-bath-200ml-677435.png?v=1740891419"},{"product_id":"luuv-natural-kids-detangling-spray-100ml","title":"LUUV Natural Kids Detangling Spray 100ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eCertified with the globally recognized ECOCERT\/COSMOS certification, this spray is a game-changer for your little one’s hair care routine. It’s time to say goodbye to stubborn tangles and hello to hassle-free styling!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eLUUV Detangle spray is specially formulated to tame even the most stubborn knots, leaving your little one’s hair silky smooth, strong, and oh-so-shiny! And let’s not forget the delightful scent! Detangling spray comes with a mouthwatering juicy pear scent that kids absolutely adore. Plus, you can rest easy knowing that the scent is naturally derived and free from any allergens. Your little one’s hair is in good hands. And now that your little one’s hair is tangle-free, it’s time to explore a whole new world of hairstyles! From cute pigtails to stylish braids, this spray opens up endless possibilities for your child’s hair adventures.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNatural and allergen-free\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFresh pear scent\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDoes not irritate skin\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eECOCERT\/COSMOS certified\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNatural origin 99,76%\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | vegan | certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eShake the bottle before use. Spray the conditioner on the hair, let it work for a few moments and comb through the hair. Can be used both on wet hair after washing and on dry hair daily.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Cetearyl Alcohol, Lecithin, Sodium Cetearyl Sulfate, Olus Oil, Propanediol, Betaine, Coconut Alkanes, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Citric Acid, Aroma\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51115375034695,"sku":null,"price":14.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-natural-kids-detangling-spray-100ml-412749.png?v=1740891417"},{"product_id":"luuv-natural-volumizing-seabuckthorn-conditioner-200ml","title":"LUUV Natural Volumizing Seabuckthorn Conditioner 200ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNatural sea buckthorn conditioner is suitable for normal\/oily hair, it gives the hair softness, volume and shine. Sea buckthorn and castor oils strengthen the hair, help to prevent hair splitting and stimulate hair growth. Wheat protein makes the hair stronger and increases volume and elasticity. Provitamin B5 makes the hair easy to comb and protects from heat treatment. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003esuitable for all hair types, including oily hair\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003egives hair fluffiness and shine\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003emoisturizes and strengthens the hair\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ewith a citrus scent\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | vegan \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply the conditioner on your hair after shampooing, starting from the tips. Leave in for 2–3 minutes, then rinse with plenty of water.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Coco-Glucoside, Betaine, Citric Acid, Xanthan Gum, Hippophae Rhamnoides (Sea Buckthorn) oil, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, PCA Glyceryl Oleate, Citrus Reticulata (Mandarin oil), Citrus Aurantium Dulcis (Orange) Oil, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Parfum, Limonene\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51115401118023,"sku":null,"price":11.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-natural-volumizing-seabuckthorn-conditioner-200ml-722591.png?v=1740891411"},{"product_id":"luuv-natural-caring-conditioner-with-plum-oil-200ml","title":"LUUV Natural Caring Conditioner With Plum Oil 200ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMaintained hair every day! Natural conditioner enriched with plum oil is perfect for daily use on all hair types. Cold-pressed plum oil moisturizes hair, restores hair ends and protects against heat treatment. The mixture of natural oils, proteins and active substances provides everything necessary for hair to be strong and shiny. Also suitable for colored hair.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli id=\"tw-target-text\" class=\"tw-data-text tw-text-large tw-ta\" dir=\"ltr\" data-placeholder=\"Tõlge\" aria-label=\"Tõlgitud tekst\" data-ved=\"2ahUKEwiX3-GDwdqGAxV6PhAIHYrmHigQ3ewLegQIBRAU\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"Y2IQFc\" lang=\"en\"\u003esuitable for all hair types, including dyed hair\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"tw-data-text tw-text-large tw-ta\" dir=\"ltr\" data-placeholder=\"Tõlge\" aria-label=\"Tõlgitud tekst\" data-ved=\"2ahUKEwiX3-GDwdqGAxV6PhAIHYrmHigQ3ewLegQIBRAU\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"Y2IQFc\" lang=\"en\"\u003ecaring and softening effect\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"tw-data-text tw-text-large tw-ta\" dir=\"ltr\" data-placeholder=\"Tõlge\" aria-label=\"Tõlgitud tekst\" data-ved=\"2ahUKEwiX3-GDwdqGAxV6PhAIHYrmHigQ3ewLegQIBRAU\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"Y2IQFc\" lang=\"en\"\u003emoisturizes and protects hair\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"tw-data-text tw-text-large tw-ta\" dir=\"ltr\" data-placeholder=\"Tõlge\" aria-label=\"Tõlgitud tekst\" data-ved=\"2ahUKEwiX3-GDwdqGAxV6PhAIHYrmHigQ3ewLegQIBRAU\"\u003e\n\u003cspan class=\"Y2IQFc\" lang=\"en\"\u003eprotects hair from heat treatment\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | vegan | paraben free\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply the conditioner on your hair after shampooing, starting from the tips. Leave in for 2–3 minutes, then rinse with plenty of water.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Distearoylethyl Dimonium Chloride, Cetearyl Alcohol, Glycerin, Cetyl alcohol, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice, Betaine, PCA Glyceryl Oleate, Prunus Domestica (Plum) Seed oil, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Guar Hydroxypropyltrimonium Chloride, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Citric Acid, Cymbopogon Martini (Palmarosa) oil, Parfum, Geraniol\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51115415961927,"sku":null,"price":11.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-natural-caring-conditioner-with-plum-oil-200ml-901624.png?v=1740891410"},{"product_id":"luuv-natural-softening-protecting-honey-conditioner-200ml","title":"LUUV Natural Softening \u0026 Protecting Honey Conditioner 200ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNatural honey conditioner makes the hair soft and easy to comb, restoring damaged hair ends. Organic honey extract makes the hair silky and protects from environmental effects. Organic barley extract stimulates hair growth and gives shine. Wheat protein strengthens the hair and increases elasticity. Also suitable for colored hair.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003esuitable for all hair types, including dyed hair\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ewith a softening and protective effect\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003egives hair softness\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eimproves hair structure and strengthens hair\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ewith a honey-sweet smell\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply the conditioner on your hair after shampooing, starting from the tips. Leave in for 2–3 minutes, then rinse with plenty of water.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Distearoylethyl Dimonium Chloride, Cetearyl Alcohol, Glycerin, Cocos Nucifera, Cetyl alcohol, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf juice, Betaine, Ricinus Communis Seed (Castor) Oil, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil, Propolis (Bee glue) extract, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Hordeum Vulgare (Barlay sprouts) Extract, Hippophae Rhamnoides (Sea Buckthorn) oil, PCA Glyceryl Oleate, Panthenol, Guar Hydroxypropyltrimonium Chloride, Coco-Glucoside, Glyceryl Oleate, Citric Acid, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Parfum  \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51115427070279,"sku":null,"price":11.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-natural-softening-protecting-honey-conditioner-200ml-904989.png?v=1740891412"},{"product_id":"luuv-natural-seabuckthorn-body-scrub-200ml","title":"LUUV Natural Seabuckthorn Body Scrub 200ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eNatural Seabuckthorn Body Scrub – your ultimate skincare indulgence for radiant, velvety-soft skin. This body scrub is expertly formulated to provide your skin with the care it truly deserves. Infused with the goodness of sea buckthorn and enriched with exfoliating particles, it offers a multi-dimensional approach to skincare. It gently removes dull, lifeless skin cells, revealing a fresh and luminous complexion. All this without causing any harm to your delicate skin.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe true beauty lies in moisturizing herbal oils. As you massage the scrub onto your skin, these oils work in harmony to lavish your body with hydration, leaving it irresistibly soft and silky. Zesty essence of orange and mandarin essential oils not only stimulate your skin but also invigorate your mind, transforming your shower routine into an awakening experience that leaves you feeling refreshed and renewed. ECOCERT \/ COSMOS eco-certificate guarantees that this body scrub is crafted with the utmost respect for nature, ensuring that your beauty regimen is as sustainable as it is effective.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eEmbrace the luxury of softness, the thrill of rejuvenation, and the enchantment of an energizing citrus symphony – all within a single jar of LUUV Natural Seabuckthorn Body Scrub.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eGentle, but effective\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cspan\u003eDoesn\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e‘\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003et dry skin\u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eRefreshing citrus aroma\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSafe for the environment\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cspan\u003eECOCERT\/COSMOS certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eKey ingredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eSeabuckthorn oil\u003c\/span\u003e is a natural super moisturizer. It contains a high concentration of fatty acids, including omega-3, omega-6, omega-7, and omega-9, which help maintain the skin’s moisture level and prevent moisture loss.\u003cbr\u003eThe high content of vitamin C in the oil makes the skin radiant and bright, helping to even out the complexion.\u003cbr\u003eThe antioxidants present in the oil, such as vitamin C, vitamin E, and beta-carotene, protect the skin from free radical damage and promote a youthful appearance.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eCarrot oil\u003c\/span\u003e (specifically carrot seed oil) contains a lot of carotene, which gives a complexion-enhancing effect. Carrot oil is always in a carrier oil (i.e., diluted) because it is too intense on its own. It contains a lot of vitamin A. The natural SPF of carrot oil is around 40, but since it is diluted, it ends up around SPF 10.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eExfoliating particles made from\u003cstrong\u003e \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003erice\u003c\/span\u003e – no plastic! The particles are not angular or sharp, so they do not damage the skin. At the same time, they are strong enough to provide a good exfoliating effect. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | vegan | certified | paraben free\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eIncorporate it into your routine once a week to maintain beautifully polished skin. Also ideal before applying self-tanning products, ensuring an even and flawless tan that lasts.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Oryza Sativa (Rice) Powder, Glycerin, Dunaliella Salina Extract, Helianthus Annus Seed Oil, Coco-Glucoside, Glyceryl Oleate, Xanthan gum, Hippophae Rhamnoides (Sea Buckthorn) oil, Citrus Aurantium Dulcis (Orange) Oil, Citrus Nobilis Peel (Mandarin) Oil, Citric Acid, Sodium benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Aroma, Citral, Linalool, Limonene\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51115441717575,"sku":null,"price":14.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-natural-seabuckthorn-body-scrub-200ml-989413.png?v=1740560026"},{"product_id":"luuv-magnesium-cream-200ml","title":"LUUV Magnesium Cream 200ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eIntroducing uplifting and rejuvenating LUUV Magnesium Cream – your gateway to a world of wellness and relaxation.  Certified with the prestigious ECOCERT\/COSMOS eco-certificate, this Magnesium Cream is a trusted and sustainable choice for your well-being. With daily use, it becomes your partner in preventing and reducing magnesium deficiency, while providing relief from muscle aches and tensions. Harnessing the power of magnesium chloride, it offers a transdermal method of absorption, allowing your body to benefit from this vital mineral in the fastest and most efficient way. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis cream is infused with the goodness of coconut oil, a natural emollient that closely resembles your skin’s own lipids. This dynamic duo ensures that even those with dry skin can absorb magnesium effectively, while providing deep hydration and nourishment. Plus, it’s suitable for even the most sensitive skin, ensuring a gentle and soothing experience for all. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFor everyday use\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePrevents\/reduces magnesium deficiency\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eRelieves muscle pain and tension\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMoisturizing and nourishing\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFor the whole family\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSuitable during pregnancy\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eECOCERT\/COSMOS\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eBeauty Shortlist Awards 2024- Wellbeing Category Gold medal\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eKey ingredients: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli id=\"tw-target-text\" class=\"tw-data-text tw-text-large tw-ta\" dir=\"ltr\" data-placeholder=\"Tõlge\" aria-label=\"Tõlgitud tekst\" data-ved=\"2ahUKEwi-ruvxp7CGAxVrExAIHSOFDeAQ3ewLegQIBRAU\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"Y2IQFc\" lang=\"en\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eMagnesium\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003ehelps muscles to relax, muscle spasms are caused by lack of magnesium. Post-workout, transdermal magnesium is best because it’s topical (you apply it to the area that strained the muscles). There are no side effects when taking topical magnesium and the effect is immediate.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"tw-data-text tw-text-large tw-ta\" dir=\"ltr\" data-placeholder=\"Tõlge\" aria-label=\"Tõlgitud tekst\" data-ved=\"2ahUKEwi-ruvxp7CGAxVrExAIHSOFDeAQ3ewLegQIBRAU\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"Y2IQFc\" lang=\"en\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eCoconut oil\u003c\/span\u003e\/coconut fat is the lightest of solid fats. With good absorption and blends well into the skin, nourishing but not heavy. Is very similar to the lipids in our own skin, so human skin absorbs it well.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"tw-data-text tw-text-large tw-ta\" dir=\"ltr\" data-placeholder=\"Tõlge\" aria-label=\"Tõlgitud tekst\" data-ved=\"2ahUKEwi-ruvxp7CGAxVrExAIHSOFDeAQ3ewLegQIBRAU\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"Y2IQFc\" lang=\"en\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eLemon essential oil\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003eis used to perfume the product, but it also has strong detox properties. Mild enough with a pleasant citrus scent. It is well suited for anti-cellulite products and for boosting the skin. Strengthens the immune system.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | vegan | certified | paraben free\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eMagnesium cream is suitable for use by the whole family and is also safe for pregnant women to use. It wonderfully helps relieve muscle tension after exercise and prevents and reduces magnesium deficiency in the body. In children, it helps relieve discomfort caused by growing pains. The cream contains magnesium chloride, which is best absorbed through the skin and also the fastest way to reduce magnesium deficiency.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Magnesium Chloride , Cocos Nucifera Oil, Polyglyceryl-3 Distearate, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate , Glyceryl stearate SE, Citrus Limon Peel (Lemon) Oil, Cymbopogon Flexuosus (Lemongrass) Oil, Mentha Piperita (Peppermint) Oil, Triethyl Citrate, Glyceryl Caprylate, Xanthan gum, Benzoic Acid, Citral, Limonene\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51115523342663,"sku":null,"price":17.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-magnesium-cream-200ml-418252.png?v=1740560025"},{"product_id":"luuv-sensitive-intimate-wash-140ml","title":"LUUV Sensitive Intimate Wash 140ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eSensitive Intimate Wash – the gentlest way to care for your most delicate areas! LUUV understands the importance of maintaining the fragile pH balance, and that’s why we’ve carefully selected herbal detergents that won’t disrupt it. With a perfectly balanced pH level of 3.5-4.5, you can trust that your intimate area will stay harmonious and healthy. Intimate wash is also completely odorless, so you can feel confident and comfortable all day long. Plus, it’s specially formulated for sensitive skin, so you can finally say goodbye to worries about irritation or redness.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSensitive Intimate Wash is certified with the leading ECOCERT\/COSMOS eco-certificate. It’s time to indulge in the forbidden fruits of paradise – the secret to feeling fresh, confident, and beautifully balanced. Make the switch today, and rediscover the joy of taking care of yourself.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eOdourless\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFor sensitive skin\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eWith dense silky foam – also suitable for shaving\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cspan\u003eECOCERT\/COSMOS certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eKey ingredients: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eCoco-Glucoside\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003eis a detergent, 100% natural (derived from coconut), environmentally friendly and certified. The detergent is gentle – also suitable for sensitive skin and children.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"Y2IQFc\" lang=\"en\"\u003e100% natural\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003ewheat protein\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003esoothes skin irritations and has an anti-inflammatory effect.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"Y2IQFc\" lang=\"en\"\u003eThe \u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eglycerin\u003c\/span\u003e we use is 100% natural and does not contain palm oil. The best feature of glycerin is that it takes moisture from the air and carries it into the skin, being able to carry it quite deeply. With a very strong moisturizing effect, and does not create a heavy\/oily feeling.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | vegan | certified | paraben free\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eSuitable for intimate parts or for the whole body.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Oryza Sativa (Rice) Starch, Coco-Glucoside, Glycerin, Glyceryl Oleate, Betaine, Cocos Nucifera, Cetyl alcohol, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Citric Acid, Xanthan gum, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51115555979591,"sku":null,"price":8.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-sensitive-intimate-wash-140ml-859869.png?v=1740560026"},{"product_id":"luuv-nourishing-honey-hand-cream-70ml","title":"LUUV Nourishing Honey Hand Cream 70ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eNourishing Honey Hand Cream – your ticket to velvety-smooth hands that feel as sweet as honey! Why settle for ordinary when you can pamper your hands with a certified ECOCERT \/ COSMOS eco-certificate product? Honey-infused hand cream is here to rescue your delicate skin and wrap it in nature’s loving embrace. This cream forms a natural shield, guarding your delicate skin from the elements and leaving you feeling confident in any weather – whether it’s battling hard water or braving harsh winds. The secret behind this is beeswax! This natural wonder ingredient not only protects your hands but also brings the sweet scent of honey to your fingertips. This hand cream is also infused with the luxurious goodness of mango butter, ensuring your hands stay perfectly hydrated.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWith continued use, you’ll notice the delightful transformation of your hand’s skin. It becomes irresistibly soft and regains its elasticity, making your hands feel youthful and rejuvenated. Nourishing Honey Hand Cream is not just a quick fix; it’s a long-term partner in keeping your paws looking and feeling their absolute best!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNourishes and moisturizes\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eForms natural protective shield\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eRich cream for the cold season\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMild honey scent\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cspan\u003eECOCERT\/COSMOS certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eWhat makes honey such an effective ingredient in cosmetics?\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"tw-data-text tw-text-large tw-ta\" dir=\"ltr\" data-placeholder=\"Tõlge\" aria-label=\"Tõlgitud tekst\" data-ved=\"2ahUKEwjjoLOBobCGAxUjFBAIHQFWBLoQ3ewLegQIDxAU\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"Y2IQFc\" lang=\"en\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eHigh sugar content\u003c\/span\u003e – ​​honey contains glucose and fructose. Sugars have many different roles, one of the most important of which is to nourish cells. When used cosmetically, it has a rejuvenating effect not only on the skin, but also on the hair.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"tw-data-text tw-text-large tw-ta\" dir=\"ltr\" data-placeholder=\"Tõlge\" aria-label=\"Tõlgitud tekst\" data-ved=\"2ahUKEwjjoLOBobCGAxUjFBAIHQFWBLoQ3ewLegQIDxAU\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"Y2IQFc\" lang=\"en\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eThe density and viscosity of honey \u003c\/span\u003e– it creates a protective barrier for our skin and plays an important role in maintaining moisture in the skin. It also creates a protective layer on wounds that allows healing without contamination.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"tw-data-text tw-text-large tw-ta\" dir=\"ltr\" data-placeholder=\"Tõlge\" aria-label=\"Tõlgitud tekst\" data-ved=\"2ahUKEwjjoLOBobCGAxUjFBAIHQFWBLoQ3ewLegQIDxAU\"\u003e\n\u003cspan class=\"Y2IQFc\" lang=\"en\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eAntibacterial properties\u003c\/span\u003e – mostly the property of honey is used for medicinal purposes. However, it can also be very useful when using cosmetics. Honey is very useful in solving problems like various skin rashes or scalp infections.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply on hands when necessary\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Cocos Nucifera Oil, Mangifera Indica seed (Mango) butter, Persea Gratissima (Avocado) oil, Polyglyceryl-3 Distearate, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate, Glycerin, Cetyl Alcohol, Triethyl Citrate, Oryza Sativa (Rice) Starch, Glyceryl Caprylate, Benzoic Acid, Cera Alba (Beeswax), Hippophae Rhamnoides Fruit Oil, Citrus Aurantium Dulcis (Orange) Oil, Xanthan Gum, Aroma, Citral, D-limonene, Linalool\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51115667849543,"sku":null,"price":11.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-nourishing-honey-hand-cream-70ml-929616.png?v=1740560027"},{"product_id":"luuv-moisturizing-hand-cream-70ml","title":"LUUV Moisturizing Hand Cream 70ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eMoisturizing Hand Cream – your daily dose of hand and nail pampering! Crafted with care and certified with the prestigious ECOCERT\/COSMOS eco-certificate, this hand cream is your eco-conscious choice for healthy and happy hands. Its light, yet deeply nourishing formula is designed to make your hands feel their absolute best. Enriched with the goodness of coconut oil, it softens and nurtures your delicate hand skin, while avocado oil provides intense hydration, ensuring your hands stay supple and moisturized all day long.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis hand cream doesn’t leave you waiting! It absorbs instantly, leaving your hands feeling irresistibly soft and silky, without any greasy residue. Its mild, fresh aroma is the perfect blend of natural fragrances that’ll uplift your mood. Treat your hands to the luxury they deserve and make Moisturizing Hand Cream your daily companion. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMoisturizes\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAbsorbs quickly\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eLight cream for daily hand care\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMild fresh aroma\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cspan\u003eECOCERT\/COSMOS certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eKey ingredients: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli data-ved=\"2ahUKEwjjoLOBobCGAxUjFBAIHQFWBLoQ3ewLegQIDxAU\" aria-label=\"Tõlgitud tekst\" data-placeholder=\"Tõlge\" dir=\"ltr\" class=\"tw-data-text tw-text-large tw-ta\"\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eCoconut oil\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003e\/coconut fat\u003c\/span\u003e is the lightest of solid fats. With good absorption and blends well into the skin, nourishing but not heavy. Is very similar to the lipids in our own skin, so human skin absorbs it well.\u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | certified | paraben free | vegan\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply on hands when necessary\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Cocos nucifera oil, Olus Oil, Polyglyceryl-3 Distearate, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate, Glycerin, Persea Gratissima oil, Triethyl Citrate, Betaine, Glyceryl Stearate SE, Oryza Sativa (Rice) Starch, Glyceryl Caprylate, Benzoic Acid, Cetyl Alcohol, Cymbopogon Flexuosus Leaf (Lemongrass) Oil, Xanthan Gum, Aroma, Citral, Linalool, Geraniol, Limonene\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51115743117639,"sku":null,"price":11.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-moisturizing-hand-cream-70ml-635051.png?v=1740560024"},{"product_id":"luuv-protecting-honey-foot-cream-70ml","title":"LUUV Protecting Honey Foot Cream 70ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eHoney Foot Cream – your ticket to happy and healthy feet!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eGet ready to pamper your feet with a product that’s not just good for you but also good for the planet. LUUV Honey Foot Cream is certified with the prestigious ECOCERT \/ COSMOS eco-certificate, ensuring you’re making a choice that’s both skin-friendly and environmentally conscious. Enriched with the natural goodness of beeswax, it creates a protective shield around your skin, keeping it hydrated and preventing it from drying out. We’ve also packed the cream with luscious mango butter and nourishing candelilla wax. Together, they work their magic to nourish your skin deeply. No more rough, cracked heels – just soft, supple, and happy feet! Add it to your daily routine, and let your feet dance through life – because you deserve nothing but the best! Your feet will thank you with every step.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNourishes and moisturizes\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eForms natural protective shield\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eRich cream for the cold season\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMild honey scent\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cspan\u003eECOCERT\/COSMOS certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eWhat makes honey such an effective ingredient in cosmetics?\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"tw-data-text tw-text-large tw-ta\" dir=\"ltr\" data-placeholder=\"Tõlge\" aria-label=\"Tõlgitud tekst\" data-ved=\"2ahUKEwjjoLOBobCGAxUjFBAIHQFWBLoQ3ewLegQIDxAU\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"Y2IQFc\" lang=\"en\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eHigh sugar content\u003c\/span\u003e – ​​honey contains glucose and fructose. Sugars have many different roles, one of the most important of which is to nourish cells. When used cosmetically, it has a rejuvenating effect not only on the skin, but also on the hair.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"tw-data-text tw-text-large tw-ta\" dir=\"ltr\" data-placeholder=\"Tõlge\" aria-label=\"Tõlgitud tekst\" data-ved=\"2ahUKEwjjoLOBobCGAxUjFBAIHQFWBLoQ3ewLegQIDxAU\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"Y2IQFc\" lang=\"en\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eThe density and viscosity of honey\u003c\/span\u003e – it creates a protective barrier for our skin and plays an important role in maintaining moisture in the skin. It also creates a protective layer on wounds that allows healing without contamination.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"tw-data-text tw-text-large tw-ta\" dir=\"ltr\" data-placeholder=\"Tõlge\" aria-label=\"Tõlgitud tekst\" data-ved=\"2ahUKEwjjoLOBobCGAxUjFBAIHQFWBLoQ3ewLegQIDxAU\"\u003e\n\u003cspan class=\"Y2IQFc\" lang=\"en\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eAntibacterial properties\u003c\/span\u003e – mostly the property of honey is used for medicinal purposes. However, it can also be very useful when using cosmetics. Honey is very useful in solving problems like various skin rashes or scalp infections.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | certified  \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply the cream to clean skin and rub until absorbed. The cream can also be used as a foot mask, take a larger amount of cream and do not rub it in completely, then put on socks and let the cream work for a while or even all night.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Mangifera Indica seed (Mango) Butter, Cocos Nucifera Oil, Glycerin, Olus Oil, Hydrogenated Vegetable Oil, Candelilla Cera, Polyglyceryl-3 Distearate, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate, Glyceryl Stearate SE, Cera Alba (Beeswax), Persea Gratissima(Avocado) oil, Triethyl Citrate, Oryza Sativa (Rice) Starch, Glyceryl Caprylate, Benzoic Acid, Hippophae Rhamnoides Fruit Oil, Citrus Aurantium Dulcis (Orange) Oil, Xanthan Gum, Aroma, Citral, D-limonene, Linalool\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51115746918727,"sku":null,"price":10.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-protecting-honey-foot-cream-70ml-664363.png?v=1740560023"},{"product_id":"luuv-natural-carrot-dry-oil-with-aloe-vera-100ml","title":"LUUV Natural Carrot Dry Oil with Aloe Vera 100ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eNatural radiant complexion without sunbathing or self-tanners? Yes, with LUUV Carrot Dry Oil, it’s possible! This dry oil is a natural vitamin bomb that deeply moisturizes your skin and restores its radiance and elasticity. The vitamin A and beta-carotene in carrot oil give your skin a beautiful healthy glow without tanning it. The dry oil is also rich in antioxidants and vitamin E, which help maintain youthful skin. Aloe has a soothing effect and provides long-lasting hydration.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe dry oil has a gel-like texture that is easily spreadable, absorbs quickly, and doesn’t leave the skin greasy or sticky. Its pleasant citrusy scent is refreshing and relaxing. LUUV Carrot Dry Oil is designed for all skin types, it doesn’t clog pores, and is great for everyday skincare. LUUV Carrot Dry Oil with aloe is natural, vegan, and contains only good ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDeeply hydrating \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eImproves skin elasticity\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eImproves complexion\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAbsorbs quickly \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNon-greasy finish\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFor all skin types\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cspan\u003eNatural SPF10\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eKey ingredients: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eCarrot oil\u003c\/span\u003e (specifically carrot seed oil) contains a lot of carotene, which gives a complexion-enhancing effect. Carrot oil is always in a carrier oil (i.e., diluted) because it is too intense on its own. It contains a lot of vitamin A. The natural SPF of carrot oil is around 40, but since it is diluted, it ends up around SPF 10.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eAloe\u003c\/span\u003e has been used in folk medicine for centuries. Aloe is an excellent moisturizer and soothes irritations, making it great for sunburn relief. Aloe has a calming effect and carries oxygen to the skin, leaving it silky and soft.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eOrange essential oil\u003c\/span\u003e is primarily used to scent the product with a fresh, sweet citrus aroma. Essential oils can penetrate the skin and provide an immediate mood-lifting, energizing feeling. Citrus oils are suitable for brightening the skin.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | paraben free | vegan\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply a suitable amount of the product to clean skin. Suitable for daily use on all skin types.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Dunaliella Salina Extract, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice, Citrus Reticulata (Mandarin Oil), Citrus Sinensis (Orange Oil), Xanthan Gum, Triethyl Citrate, Sodium benzoate, Potassium sorbate, Glyceryl Caprylate, Citric Acid, Benzoic Acid, Parfum, Citral, Limonene, Linalool\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51115752456519,"sku":null,"price":19.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-natural-carrot-dry-oil-with-aloe-vera-100ml-860544.png?v=1740560025"},{"product_id":"luuv-shimmering-carrot-dry-oil-bronze-100ml","title":"LUUV Shimmering Carrot Dry Oil Bronze 100ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eBronze, shimmering skin is just within reach! LUUV Shimmering Carrot Dry Oil is an aloe-based, richly moisturizing vitamin bomb that gives the skin an eye-catching, beautiful gleam. The carrot oil, rich in vitamin A and beta-carotene, makes the skin beautifully radiant without a self-tanning effect.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe antioxidants and vitamin E in carrot oil help maintain the skin’s youthful appearance, while aloe soothes and deeply moisturizes the skin, helping to maintain its moisture level. The skin remains silky soft, elastic, vibrant, and radiant. The dry oil contains light-reflecting mica particles that gently shimmer and are safe for both the skin and the environment. It is ideal for all skin types, does not clog pores, and is suitable for daily use. The gel-like texture of the dry oil glides effortlessly over the skin, absorbs quickly, and does not leave the skin sticky or greasy.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDeeply moisturizes\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eImproves skin elasticity\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eEnhances complexion\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eGel-like texture\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAbsorbs quickly\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWashable sparkle\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSuitable for all skin types\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNatural SPF 10\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eKey ingredients: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eCarrot oil\u003c\/span\u003e (specifically carrot seed oil) contains a lot of carotene, which gives a complexion-enhancing effect. Carrot oil is always in a carrier oil (i.e., diluted) because it is too intense on its own. It contains a lot of vitamin A. The natural SPF of carrot oil is around 40, but since it is diluted, it ends up around SPF 10.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eAloe\u003c\/span\u003e has been used in folk medicine for centuries. Aloe is an excellent moisturizer and soothes irritations, making it great for sunburn relief. Aloe has a calming effect and carries oxygen to the skin, leaving it silky and soft.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eOrange essential oil\u003c\/span\u003e is primarily used to scent the product with a fresh, sweet citrus aroma. Essential oils can penetrate the skin and provide an immediate mood-lifting, energizing feeling. Citrus oils are suitable for brightening the skin.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWe use caramel for coloring (in self-tanning mousse and bronze dry oil). It is a 100% natural colorant with a pleasant caramel aroma, making it an eco-friendly choice.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | paraben free | vegan\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eShake the bottle before use. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eApply an appropriate amount of the product to clean skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Dunaliella Salina Extract, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice, Citrus Nobilis (Mandarin) Peel Oil, Citrus Aurantium (Orange) Peel Oil, Xanthan Gum, Triethyl Citrate, Glyceryl Caprylate, Benzoic Acid, Mica, Titanium Dioxide (CI 77891), Raphanus Sativus (Radish) Root Extract, Citric Acid, Maltodextrin, Parfum, Citral, Limonene, Linalool\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51115764482375,"sku":null,"price":20.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-shimmering-carrot-dry-oil-bronze-100ml-155486.png?v=1740560028"},{"product_id":"luuv-natural-conditioner-for-kids-200ml","title":"LUUV Natural Conditioner For Kids 200ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eThis enchanting conditioner deeply moisturizes, nourishes, and protects the hair, leaving it irresistibly shiny. LUUV children’s hair conditioner is certified with the prestigious ECOCERT\/COSMOS eco-certificate.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSay goodbye to tangles and hello to effortlessly smooth and manageable hair! Conditioner strengthens hair from roots to ends, making it easy to comb and wonderfully lightweight. Infused with natural oils and betaine, it deeply moisturizes and enhances the overall health and beauty of the hair. And let’s not forget about that enchanting vanilla aroma! It’s derived from natural sources and is completely allergen-free. If your little one dreams of becoming the next Rapunzel with long, flowing locks, LUUV natural conditioner for kids is the perfect choice!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNatural and allergen-free\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSweet vanilla scent\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDoes not irritate skin\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eECOCERT\/COSMOS certified\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNatural origin 98,72%\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | vegan | certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e  Use the conditioner after shampoo and apply from the ends only. Let it sit and rinse! You can use the conditioner after every wash.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Aqua, Cetearyl Alcohol, Lecithin, Sodium Cetearyl Sulfate, Olus Oil, Cetyl Alcohol, Betaine, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Citric Acid, Aroma\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52138032202055,"sku":null,"price":11.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-natural-conditioner-for-kids-200ml-2844222.jpg?v=1756222791"},{"product_id":"luuv-deodorant-citrus-bliss-50ml","title":"LUUV Deodorant Citrus Bliss 50ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eCitrus natural deodorant with deodorizing agents that ensure you feel fresh, cheerful, and energized all day long. With 24-hour proven protection against unpleasant odors.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe deodorant allows the skin to breathe freely and does not interfere with its natural functions or clog pores. LUUV's secret weapons are sweat-absorbing rice starch and antibacterial sage extract. Additionally, the deodorant contains moisturizing and soothing aloe vera, gently nurturing underarm skin. The harmonious blend of citrus essential oils creates a delightful scent bouquet.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDries quickly and leaves no stains on clothes. And best of all, the deodorant is free from aluminum, alcohol, and baking soda, and is 100% vegan!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e24h protection\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eEnergizing citrus scent\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNon-irritating\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNon-comedogenic\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMoisturizes and soothes\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePreserves skin’s natural function\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFree from soda, alcohol, and aluminum\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | paraben free | vegan\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Apply to clean underarms. Use daily.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Aqua, Zinc Ricinoleate, Tetrasodium Glutamate Diacetate,Oryza Sativa (Rice) Starch, Propanediol, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice, Triethyl Citrate, Polyglyceryl-3-Caprylate, Salvia Officinalis Leaf Extract, Citric acid, Citrus Aurantium Dulcis Oil (Orange oil), Glyceryl Caprylate, Benzoic Acid, Xanthan Gum, Parfum, Limonene, Linalool, Citral, Benzyl Salicylate, Hydroxycitronellal, Hexyl Cinnamal, Geraniol\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52138062283079,"sku":null,"price":11.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-deodorant-citrus-bliss-50ml-1045610.png?v=1756222797"},{"product_id":"luuv-deodorant-soothing-comfort-50ml","title":"LUUV Deodorant Soothing Comfort 50ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eLUUV Soothing deodorant with natural deodorizing agents prevents the formation of body odor and absorbs excess sweat. With 24 hours of proven protection, you can feel fresh and energized all day long!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDeodorant does not disrupt the skin’s natural functioning and does not clog pores. Rice starch in the deodorant absorbs sweat, while sage extract has antibacterial properties. Additionally, it contains moisturizing aloe vera, which nourishes and soothes the skin under the arms – an ideal choice for sensitive skin! The deodorant dries quickly and does not leave stains on clothes. The organic and enchanting floral scent refreshes both body and mind.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSoothing deodorant is free from aluminum, alcohol, and baking soda, and is 100% vegan!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e24h protection\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePleasent mild floral scent\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNon-irritating\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNon-comedogenic\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMoisturizes and soothes\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePreserves skin’s natural function\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFree from soda, alcohol and aluminum\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | paraben free | vegan\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Apply to clean underarms. Use daily.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Aqua, Zinc Ricinoleate, Tetrasodium Glutamate Diacetate, Oryza Sativa (Rice) Starch, Propanediol, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice, Triethyl Citrate,Polyglyceryl-3-Caprylate, Salvia Officinalis Leaf Extract, Citric acid, Cymbopogon Martini (Palmarosa) oil, Glyceryl Caprylate, Benzoic Acid, Xanthan Gum, Parfum, Geraniol, Linalool, Limonene, Citral\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52138114416967,"sku":null,"price":11.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-deodorant-soothing-comfort-50ml-7238915.png?v=1756222794"},{"product_id":"luuv-deodorant-lemongrass-green-50ml","title":"LUUV Deodorant Lemongrass Green 50ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eLUUV Unisex deodorant with natural deodorizing agents prevents the formation of body odor and keeps you fresh and dry all day long!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe unisex deodorant allows the skin to function naturally and does not clog pores. Rice starch in the deodorant absorbs sweat, sage extract combats odor-causing bacteria, and aloe moisturizes and soothes delicate underarm skin. The deodorant dries quickly and does not leave stains on clothes. The fresh blend of essential oils is suitable for both men and women.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe Unisex deodorant is certified with the globally recognized ECOCERT\/COSMOS certification, so you can be sure you’re using a product that’s not only good for you but also for our planet. Additionally, it is aluminum-free, alcohol-free, and soda-free, and 100% vegan!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e24h protection \u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFresh scent that is suitable for both men and women \u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNon-irritating \u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNon-comedogenic\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMoisturizes and soothes\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePreserves skin’s natural function\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFree from soda, alcohol, and aluminum\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | paraben free | vegan | certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Apply to clean underarms. Use daily.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Aqua, Zinc Ricinoleate, Tetrasodium Glutamate Diacetate, Oryza Sativa (Rice) Starch, Propanediol, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice, Triethyl Citrate, Polyglyceryl-3-Caprylate, Salvia Officinalis Leaf Extract, Citric acid, Citrus Limon Peel (Lemon) Oil, Cymbopogon Flexuosus (Lemongrass) Oil, Citrus Aurantium Bergamia Fruit (Bergamot) Oil, Glyceryl Caprylate, Benzoic Acid, Xanthan Gum, Limonene, Citral, Linalool, Geraniol\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52138263904583,"sku":null,"price":11.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-deodorant-lemongrass-green-50ml-1178078.png?v=1756222794"},{"product_id":"luuv-deodorant-fresh-breeze-50ml","title":"LUUV Deodorant Fresh Breeze 50ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eLUUV Fresh deodorant with natural deodorizing agents prevents the formation of body odor and keeps you fresh and dry all day long!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDeodorant allows the skin to breathe freely, does not disrupt the skin’s natural functioning, and does not clog pores. Rice starch in the deodorant absorbs sweat, while antibacterial sage extract combats odor-causing bacteria. Moisturizing and soothing aloe vera nourishes delicate underarm skin. The deodorant dries quickly and leaves no stains on your favorite clothes. The blend of green tea and lemon essential oils refreshes and invigorates both body and mind.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eOur deodorant is free from aluminum, alcohol, and baking soda, and is 100% vegan!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e24h protection\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFresh “green” scent\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNon-irritating\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNon-comedogenic\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMoisturizes and soothes\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePreserves skin’s natural function\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFree from soda, alcohol, and aluminum\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | paraben free | vegan\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Apply to clean underarms. Use daily.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Aqua, Dunaliella Salina Extract, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice, Citrus Nobilis (Mandarin) Peel Oil, Citrus Aurantium (Orange) Peel Oil, Xanthan Gum, Triethyl Citrate, Glyceryl Caprylate, Benzoic Acid, Mica, Titanium Dioxide (CI 77891), Raphanus Sativus (Radish) Root Extract, Citric Acid, Maltodextrin, Parfum, Citral, Limonene, Linalool\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52138317152583,"sku":null,"price":11.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-deodorant-fresh-breeze-50ml-6627868.png?v=1756222791"}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/collections\/luuv-629779.jpg?v=1739979842","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/collections\/luuv.oembed","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}